You acknowledge that you own nothing in the Software itself; you merely have the right to use it under this License.

### 2.2 Ownership of Your Data

Your traffic data, configuration files, and operational information remain your exclusive property. You hereby grant Licensor a limited license to:

- Process your data to provide the Software and services
- Store your data on systems operated by Licensor (local or cloud, as applicable)
- Use aggregated, anonymized, and statistically de-identified data to improve the Software and services (opt-out available)
- Access your data as necessary to provide support, maintenance, and security services

Licensor will not sell, rent, or disclose your data to third parties without your explicit consent, except as required by law.

### 2.3 Data Privacy & Ownership

You retain full ownership and control of your traffic data. You may:
- Export your data at any time in standard formats
- Delete your data permanently (30-day retention for compliance only)
- Restrict use of your data for product improvement
- Revoke Licensor's access to your data (except for historical backup)

### 2.4 No License to Patents

This Agreement does not grant any license to Licensor's patents, patent applications, or patent rights. Use of the Software may require licenses or authorizations from third parties for certain patented technologies.

